{"tid":576680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（說書人）今日我講既係劏房波慘被數十大漢強姦既故事","createTime":"2018-03-01T05:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T21:42:52.000Z","uid":37666,"like":152,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7102229a0665a5f5d4dae6ddc6e3714db5bc95","tid":576680,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"哎，今次呢個貪官都算抵死咯，畀人剝曬衫褲剝曬底褲。<br />\n話說呢個劏房波，畀人拖咗去泥漿度去打喎，仲塞佢食屎添呀<br />\n佢食下，食下呢，又食得幾過癮喎，佢猛咁食，猛咁食，覺得好過癮好過癮"},{"pid":"ee0a329df86ba7249e043c9ad3420313a9e74a33","tid":576680,"uid":26752,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩 玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97628a36c9eed53090fdee58094cd5398f6f4c6","tid":576680,"uid":37666,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ee0a329df86ba7249e043c9ad3420313a9e74a33","tid":576680,"uid":26752,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩 玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲狗官係咁cheap架啦"},{"pid":"f1ca76b2e0c0c0d223bbb24a5106f41074739a0f","tid":576680,"uid":50101,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"我又唔信個個都咁憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7548c79cfab02e6c540d117a6a1db2157f5dec6","tid":576680,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97628a36c9eed53090fdee58094cd5398f6f4c6","tid":576680,"uid":37666,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ee0a329df86ba7249e043c9ad3420313a9e74a33","tid":576680,"uid":26752,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩 玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲狗官係咁cheap架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"賤格<img src=\"/a