3","tid":576680,"uid":37666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"陳茂波原來又係基督徒<br />\n啲死耶撚正仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"講下教會朋友換妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個女做中聯辦公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:46:47.000Z","msg":"集中火力屌個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700ed9d74574ea5ae7859a91a6b156e6c7fa4833","tid":576680,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"追故中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49705c6447d661ff3d81b0846318475866f5c65f","tid":576680,"uid":37666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"話說呢個劏房波份預算案激嬲全世界，真係人見人打<br />\n<br />\n有次仲沖緊涼比班地盤佬衝左入黎雞姦喎，仲姦足十日呀<br />\n哇！可憐囉今次，原來佢個性病剛剛先好番，今次屎忽又開花<br />\n<br />\n到左第二日條雜種狗諗下諗下日日比人屌屎忽唔係辦法架喎<br />\n呀個廢柴居然走去開記者會哭訴喎！好啦咁聽下佢講咩啦<br />\n<br />\n咁佢就話啦，佢份工原先係諗住威先至爭返黎，點會諗到咁難做呢<br />\n佢仲話喎班蟻民難服侍喎，仲話自己好努力貪污架麻咁都比人鬧唔做野<br />\n<br />\n記者會最後仲喊到死狗咁，真係陰公囉～啲小市民<br />\n<br />\n咁個記者會都未完成班記者衝哂上去打佢，呢個劏房波仲唔走佬咩<br />\n<br />\n點知佢去到邊就比人打到邊，打到佢腫成個波咁真係低死囉"},{"pid":"0cee5d129d50d657d8de9f087e8efcbd3154ae42","tid":576680,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a2c12af79e5c7825ade8e88f284c5b2e5ce369","tid":576680,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T08:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},